title: Martyrd - Mortal Coil [2011][mp3-320]_infx222
description:
If you love metal, you'll LOVE Martyrd. These guys know what they're doing; combining technical skill, melodic musicality, and raw energy, Martyrd more than lives up to the expectations of a metal band in the modern era. "The Mortal Coil" expands the horizons for what metal music has become, mixing progressive sounds with the thrash influences of the early 80's.
